{"TopicId":5346,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to post pics without attaching them?","CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T15:14:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T15:14:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI know. You\\\u0027re going to \u003Cem\u003Ehate\u003C/em\u003E me for not knowing this. But could someone please tell me how to post pictures using the \u003Cimg src=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022%7Boption%7D\u0022\u003E thing? Thanks.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Victor","CreatedById":609,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T15:19:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003EYou will have to use the img-tag. You begin with [img], then the url and then the closing tag, [/IMG]\u003Cbr\u003EExample:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E[img=http://img685.imageshack.us/img685/2424/794881.jpg]\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EResult:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img685.imageshack.us/img685/2424/794881.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022794881.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spoot Knight","CreatedById":8302,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T15:23:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHost them with a site such as Imageshack, Photobucket, or Imgur, to name a few.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T16:10:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI use flickr. But when I try, this happens:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u0022 alt=\u00226659736051\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELink to image I was trying to share:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spoot Knight","CreatedById":8302,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T16:16:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOkay I have no idea how Flickr works.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryten","CreatedById":348,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T16:21:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E Right click on the image, then select one of the sizes. Then right click on the image that appears, and click \\\u0027copy image URL\\\u0027, or whatever your browser\\\u0027s equivalent is. This is the URL you need to put into the tags, not the page URL. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EExample-the medium 640 picture.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7005/6659736051_d2f3e307ab_z.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00226659736051_d2f3e307ab_z.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T16:32:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh. Thanks a lot! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7148/6659739143_9d15dcec9b_b.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00226659739143_9d15dcec9b_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Victor","CreatedById":609,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T16:33:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mincespy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022mincespy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI use flickr. But when I try, this happens:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u0022 alt=\u00226659736051\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEvery image that you embedd using the img-tag needs to end with .jpg or another image-extension.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELink to image I was trying to share:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.flickr.com/photos/73063837@N03/6659736051/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scruce","CreatedById":9059,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-11T21:34:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFlickr is quite difficult to get the images, you have to narrow it down so it shows a .jpg as it\\\u0027s ending. This can be difficult, however it is possible.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EExample Flickr image embeds just fine:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6223/6313048774_fda6688e54_b.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00226313048774_fda6688e54_b.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}